# 🔐 Multi-Algorithm Text Encryption Tool (Python)

This Python tool allows you to encrypt and decrypt text using three encryption algorithms:

- **AES** (Advanced Encryption Standard)
- **DES** (Data Encryption Standard)
- **RSA** (Rivest-Shamir-Adleman)

## 🛠️ Features

- **AES Encryption**: Uses CBC mode with random keys.
- **DES Encryption**: Uses ECB mode with random keys.
- **RSA Encryption**: Public/Private key encryption.

---

## 🚀 Usage

1. Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/encryption-tool.git
cd encryption-tool
